From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Galileo CSM Workspace <galileo-csm@example.invalid>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 17:45:00 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] QuarkPlatformPkg: make CSM boot targets visible

Keep the Boot Manager visible at startup, store legacy boot options in
the GenericBds/rEFInd-compatible BBS_TABLE plus BbsIndex format, migrate
older two-byte BbsIndex options in place, and add USB mass-storage BBS
entries so CSM-aware boot managers can see present USB disks.

